See critical note.

	<DIV CLASS="mynote">
	<P CLASS="b0 a0 justify small italic">
The critical note to the Greek text (<SPAN LANG="el" CLASS="Greek">φησὶ δ’ αὐτὴν Θεόπομπος πρώτους Μιλησίους κτίσαι, . . . Καππαδοκῶν ἄρχοντα, τρίτον</SPAN>) reads:
	<P CLASS="i1 b0 a0 justify">
Certainly one or more words have fallen out here. <SPAN CLASS="manuscript">i</SPAN> inserts <SPAN LANG="el" CLASS="Greek">καί</SPAN>, and <SPAN CLASS="manuscript">oz</SPAN> <SPAN LANG="el" CLASS="Greek">καὶ εἶτα</SPAN>.
	</P></DIV>


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
