	</A>
and
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/15A2*.html#1.30.6
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
15.1.30</A>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note115" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/12C*.html#ref115
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">115</A>
<I>Roman</I> province of course.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note116" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/12C*.html#ref116
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">116</A>
"Pompey's city." On the history of this city, see J. G. C. Anderson in <I>Anatolian Studies presented to Sir <A ID="p451x"></A>William Mitchell Ramsay</I>, p6. Anderson's article is of great importance in the study of the time of composition of Strabo's <I>Geography</I>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note117" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/12C*.html#ref117
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">117</A>
Mt. "Realgar (red sulphuret of arsenic) mine."


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note118" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/12C*.html#ref118
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">118</A>
Hence the continual necessity of purchasing other slaves to replace them.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note119" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/12C*.html#ref119
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">119</A>
<I>i.e.</I> as being divided up into several domains.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note120" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/12C*.html#ref120
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">120</A>
<I>i.e.</I> "Founder" of Pontus as an independent kingdom; reigned 337‑302 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN>


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note121" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/12C*.html#ref121
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">121</A>
<I>Cf.</I> the "dug mullets" in Celtica,
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/4A*.html#1.6.7
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
4.1.6</A>.



